Q: Why does my in-game override not work?
A∶ If the in-game overlay does not work, the following may solve the problem.
1. Close the client, right-click the startup icon and select "Run as administrator";
2. Check the settings and make sure the "In-game overlay" is enabled in the "Voice Attachment" item;
3. Check the game display settings and change the "full screen" of the game to "borderless window".
